## Complete `@media print` template

```css
@media print {
  @page {
    margin: 0;
    size: Letter portrait; /* DEFAULT — override only if user specifies */
  }

  * {
    -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
    print-color-adjust: exact;
  }

  body {
    background: white;
    padding: 10mm;
    min-height: unset; /* remove 100vh if set */
    -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
    print-color-adjust: exact;
  }

  .page {
    box-shadow: none;
    border-radius: 0;
    width: 100%;
    -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
    print-color-adjust: exact;
  }

  h2, h3 {
    page-break-after: avoid;
  }

  .card, .section {
    page-break-inside: avoid;
  }

  nav, .sidebar, button, .no-print {
    display: none;
  }
}
```

